  "reference_number": "GAC0063",
  "remarks": "\nMukesh VAYA is an involved person within the meaning of the Global Anti-Corruption Sanctions regulations 2021 on the basis of the following grounds: (1) VAYA is associated with a person involved in serious corruption, namely Kamlesh PATTNI; (2) VAYA is or has been involved in facilitating or providing support for serious corruption. Specifically, VAYA has facilitated or provided support for the serious corruption of Kamlesh PATTNI.   \n",
